tweets.text:
Last week, I activated the Florida Small Business Emergency Bridge Loan Program to help small businesses impacted by #HurricaneIan. 

Today we awarded $2.5 million in loans to 55 small businesses so they can get back on their feet.

Apply for aid here: https://t.co/vkTEpFqEUg

entity.description: The 2022 Atlantic hurricane season began on June 1 and comes to an end on November 30.
